#

BBQ Pulled Pork Sliders with Coleslaw

$25
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 12

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinComfort Food

Tags:

EasyFamily-FriendlySlow Cooker

Description

Tender, slow-cooked pulled pork smothered in tangy BBQ sauce, served on soft slider buns with a crunchy coleslaw.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 3 lbs
  • BBQ sauce: 1 cup
  • Slider buns: 12
  • Cabbage: 2 cups
  • Carrots: 1 cup
  • Mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • Apple cider vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • Sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
